=head2 cfg_index_date_format

 cfg_index_date_format

This is the date format that will be used to group the entries
by in the C<intermixed_index> template. Every time the formatting
of a story's date using this template is different from the
previous one, an C<h1> header of the C<index_date> class with
be emitted.

=cut
%y-%m-%d